fal-ai/framepack.name: Framepack
fal-ai/framepack.description: Framepack is an efficient Image-to-video model that autoregressively generates videos.

prompt.description: Text prompt for video generation (max 500 characters).

seed.description: The seed to use for generating the video.

aspect_ratio.description: The aspect ratio of the video to generate.

resolution.description: The resolution of the video to generate. 720p generations cost 1.5x more than 480p generations.

cfg_scale.description: Classifier-Free Guidance scale for the generation.

num_frames.description: The number of frames to generate.

enable_safety_checker.description: If set to true, the safety checker will be enabled.

fal-ai/flux-pro.name: FLUX.1 [pro]
fal-ai/flux-pro.description: FLUX.1 [pro] is a professional-grade model that generates premium quality images from text, optimized for commercial applications and professional creative workflows.

prompt.description: The prompt to generate an image from.

image_size.description: The size of the generated image.

num_inference_steps.description: The number of inference steps to perform.

seed.description: The same seed and the same prompt given to the same version of the model will output the same image every time.

guidance_scale.description: The CFG (Classifier Free Guidance) scale is a measure of how close you want the model to stick to your prompt when looking for a related image to show you.

sync_mode.description: If set to true, the function will wait for the image to be generated and uploaded before returning the response.

num_images.description: The number of images to generate.

safety_tolerance.description: The safety tolerance level for the generated image. 1 being the most strict and 5 being the most permissive.

output_format.description: The format of the generated image.
